Confirming successful installation. This is how I did it:

Navigate to where you downloaded the torrent. Select the first .rar file and unpack it into the same folder where everything is. Mount the .iso that you just unpacked (I used Daemon Tools). When it prompts you select View All Files. Navigate down to Setup. NOT AcroSetup, this is something different. When it asks for the CD Key use the one posted on the bottom of page six, it works fine.

After that you're all set =)
